    "password": "%(encrypted_password)s"
}

The response body of change password V2 API is below:

{
    "changePassword" : {
        "adminPass" : "%(password)s"
    }
}

The response body of change password V3 API is below:

{
    "change_password" : {
        "admin_password" : "%(password)s"
    }
}

